metadata.description:
Who's gonna rock the party? Banneroos will totally 
rock the party... like fricken hard yo. Banneroos have
come to Earth from the planet Banneros to put on 
the most epic music festival ever. Why? Because they 
want to party with us of course! With 8 different 
stages, flying objects, and close to 200 properties, 
we all need to party with Banneroos to have a good
time.... all the time... 
​
​
​
